#. Key:	19326DC04FE379B56BC4D2905E534E29
msgctxt ",19326DC04FE379B56BC4D2905E534E29"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Neither is the Titanic?! Jack and Rose never existed</>"
