msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>You know... Why does it even matter? Can't the Titanic and The Matrix just be two different movies and.. you know.. Co-exist?</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Alltså... varför spelar det ens någon roll? Kan inte Titanic och The Matrix bara vara två olika filmer och... du vet... samexistera?</>"

#. Key:	3A50B66540D21984FBBC56B4B4BD24AC
msgctxt ",3A50B66540D21984FBBC56B4B4BD24AC"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Might've been a dumb argument but I would any day of the week have that argument again than talk to Rick.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Det kanske var ett dumt argument, men jag hade hellre haft det argumentet igen vilken dag som helst än pratat med Rick.</>"

