#. Key:	D1EAA0A64E9D675792C0818183464930
msgctxt ",D1EAA0A64E9D675792C0818183464930"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Listen, I'm not saying this is normal. It creeps me out just hearing about it. But if you really want to investigate this. Find your evidence and report it to the Forest Service, I don't want you to get in trouble out here digging up someone else's secrets.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Lyssna, jag säger inte att det här är normalt. Det ger mig kalla kårar bara att höra om det. Men om du verkligen vill undersöka det här, hitta dina bevis och rapportera det till Skogstjänsten. Jag vill inte att du hamnar i trubbel här ute för att du gräver i någon annans hemligheter.</>"

#. Key:	CA500C03432FFBF2EF0207B6F8D47980
msgctxt ",CA500C03432FFBF2EF0207B6F8D47980"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Yeah you should, see you in the morning!</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Ja, det borde du. Vi hörs i morgon bitti!</>"

#. Key:	82A22916473B682D20EE0D9E9BC95843
msgctxt ",82A22916473B682D20EE0D9E9BC95843"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Rick...I think your radio cut off...Hello? Hello!?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Rick... jag tror radion bröts... Hallå? Hallå!?</>"

#. Key:	E983374C481543BEC90D33984F536FE8
msgctxt ",E983374C481543BEC90D33984F536FE8"
msgid "<Speech>Rick...</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Rick...</>"

#. Key:	8F0BE43E4E9781AE2CD2CE84F23EAEB4
msgctxt ",8F0BE43E4E9781AE2CD2CE84F23EAEB4"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Also, second point. There's been an increased amount of reports of wildlife, specifically within sector 2. So make sure you bring your bear spray with you if you decide to go hiking. And reports any more sightings directly to the Forest Service.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Och punkt två. Det har kommit in fler rapporter om vilda djur, särskilt inom sektor 2. Så se till att ta med björnspray om du bestämmer dig för att vandra. Och rapportera alla fler observationer direkt till Skogstjänsten.</>"

#. Key:	38ACF37D4B9A6CEE07C991B554C94DF2
msgctxt ",38ACF37D4B9A6CEE07C991B554C94DF2"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hello Rick? Does the radio work now?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hallå Rick? Fungerar radion nu?</>"

