msgctxt ",FA2338BC4BEE4B85B71E058D40178DE1"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>He's been alright, but Rick you know....he's Rick.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Han har varit okej, men Rick, du vet... han är Rick.</>"

#. Key:	97D93Kailyn64A53660F989430BC3CA0F840
msgctxt ",97D93Kailyn64A53660F989430BC3CA0F840"
msgid "<Speech>He's been alright</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Han har varit okej</>"

#. Key:	4AA13D0442Kailyn5860EDDAEBA8F35C9B86
msgctxt ",4AA13D0442Kailyn5860EDDAEBA8F35C9B86"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>That's the spirit! How's Rick been treating? Not too many jobs I hope.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Det är rätt inställning! Hur har Rick behandlat dig? Inte för många jobb hoppas jag.</>"

#. Key:	637C4E1B4B23ED290478AEBBC9338C21
msgctxt ",637C4E1B4B23ED290478AEBBC9338C21"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Has he always been like this?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Har han alltid varit så här?</>"

#. Key:	2D7911CD43FDDF093A0CBAA1D30E714A
msgctxt ",2D7911CD43FDDF093A0CBAA1D30E714A"
msgid "<Speech>Has he always been like this?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Har han alltid varit så här?</>"

#. Key:	A44257924E58729790D05F85DDDAF41C
msgctxt ",A44257924E58729790D05F85DDDAF41C"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Yeah, I know. I've been working with him for a long time. You'll get used to him.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Ja, jag vet. Jag har jobbat med honom länge. Du vänjer dig vid honom.</>"

#. Key:	4029B773410417C0EBA3E7B305AF3DBC
msgctxt ",4029B773410417C0EBA3E7B305AF3DBC"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Disappeared? Someone disappeared here? I haven't heard about that.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Försvann? Försvann någon här? Det har jag inte hört något om.</>"

#. Key:	3798A64948E3202AFB095984DF871D7D
msgctxt ",3798A64948E3202AFB095984DF871D7D"
msgid "<Speech>Disappeared?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Försvann?</>"

#. Key:	358F1BBA44359A9EBE53D5AC1C82E914
msgctxt ",358F1BBA44359A9EBE53D5AC1C82E914"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Well...not always, I think he was way more laid-back and  easy-going when I first started. But after the disappearing of Thomas, he hasn't been the same.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Tja... inte alltid. Jag tror han var mycket mer avslappnad och lättsam när jag började. Men efter Thomas försvinnande har han inte varit densamma.</>"

#. Key:	D299AE3248A7D492C5CD85BA9BDB933E
msgctxt ",D299AE3248A7D492C5CD85BA9BDB933E"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah, you don't say... So what happened?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Ja, det menar du inte... Så vad hände?</>"

#. Key:	5370E66647C5BBB88495E59719B6EAB6
msgctxt ",5370E66647C5BBB88495E59719B6EAB6"
msgid "<Speech>You don't say</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Det menar du inte</>"

#. Key:	72BB03074351EABCFF27A59C34FB5290
msgctxt ",72BB03074351EABCFF27A59C34FB5290"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Seriously? That's something they really should include when you sign up.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Seriöst? Det är något de verkligen borde ta med när man skriver på.</>"

#. Key:	71D5749D4195A92579158CA6796B52AD
msgctxt ",71D5749D4195A92579158CA6796B52AD"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Shit... so the tower is completely empty now?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Fan... så tornet står helt tomt nu?</>"

#. Key:	8043C36D40803D00A287A1BE2438DEAF
msgctxt ",8043C36D40803D00A287A1BE2438DEAF"
msgid "<Speech>So the tower is completely empty now?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Så tornet står helt tomt nu?</>"

#. Key:	ECA0C1B24B0486AB873E26B3C904E9D2
msgctxt ",ECA0C1B24B0486AB873E26B3C904E9D2"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>No clue, it was just a regular evening when he suddenly stopped answering the radio. Rick headed over to his tower to check on him and just like that, he was gone. Everything was still in his tower except him.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Ingen aning, det var bara en vanlig kväll när han plötsligt slutade svara på radion. Rick gick över till hans torn för att kolla till honom och så var han bara borta. Allt fanns fortfarande kvar i hans torn utom han själv.</>"

#. Key:	AE063BC641CE2CC1D54822BC8AE52643
msgctxt ",AE063BC641CE2CC1D54822BC8AE52643"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>I'll keep that mind. But did no one go look for him?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Det ska jag komma ihåg. Men gick ingen och letade efter honom?</>"

#. Key:	7EBAA2624AED8986792A36BF5AF247D4
msgctxt ",7EBAA2624AED8986792A36BF5AF247D4"
msgid "<Speech>I'll keep that mind.</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Det ska jag komma ihåg.</>"

#. Key:	00D1909A4EB02EC009667CA0D8184B3E
msgctxt ",00D1909A4EB02EC009667CA0D8184B3E"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Yep...completely abandoned... I've tried asking him about it, but he has just told me that it has been closed down due to lack of funds. He really doesn't like talking about it, so I wouldn't mention it.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Japp... helt övergivet... Jag har försökt fråga honom om det, men han har bara sagt att det stängts på grund av brist på pengar. Han gillar verkligen inte att prata om det, så jag skulle inte nämna det.</>"

#. Key:	36114D2341978950B334EA86A9D20C26
msgctxt ",36114D2341978950B334EA86A9D20C26"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Hello?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Hallå?</>"

#. Key:	40B9CD74471C58493E47DBB67807B4Kailyn
msgctxt ",40B9CD74471C58493E47DBB67807B4Kailyn"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Doesn't...that scare you?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Skrämmer inte... det dig?</>"

#. Key:	8B90463243853EC99B6DACBF0A3A6EA9
msgctxt ",8B90463243853EC99B6DACBF0A3A6EA9"
msgid "<Speech>Doesn't...that scare you?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Skrämmer inte... det dig?</>"

#. Key:	2D5C2DCD48308732873F4CA60452A509
msgctxt ",2D5C2DCD48308732873F4CA60452A509"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Yeah, there were lots of search parties but nothing ever turned up, no clues, no tracks, no nothing.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Ja, det var massor av skallgångar men inget dök någonsin upp. Inga ledtrådar, inga spår, ingenting.</>"

#. Key:	AC1B6AEE4E19EEA32B6B01B6DDA51FF5
msgctxt ",AC1B6AEE4E19EEA32B6B01B6DDA51FF5"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>You sure he went lost?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Är du säker på att han gick vilse?</>"

#. Key:	175530E94150Kailyn2BFD1C46BD63D30A0B
msgctxt ",175530E94150Kailyn2BFD1C46BD63D30A0B"
msgid "<Speech>Sure he went lost?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Säker på att han gick vilse?</>"

#. Key:	AAB332FA407D1BECA51FAB96F335285F
msgctxt ",AAB332FA407D1BECA51FAB96F335285F"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>That's great for you, but I sure don't</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Vad bra för dig, men jag gör det verkligen inte</>"

#. Key:	86E7D2534739430EE5C15F9FF5D42D31
msgctxt ",86E7D2534739430EE5C15F9FF5D42D31"
msgid "<Speech>That's great for you</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Vad bra för dig</>"

#. Key:	95448E12416DA5A974AD8A9995A83CF8
msgctxt ",95448E12416DA5A974AD8A9995A83CF8"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Like the back of your hand, you say? Any advice on where not to go?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Som din egen ficka, säger du? Några råd om var man inte ska gå?</>"

#. Key:	7EF365204484068D876AC0B24F754793
msgctxt ",7EF365204484068D876AC0B24F754793"
msgid "<Speech>Any advice where not to go?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Några råd om var man inte ska gå?</>"

#. Key:	DAE1EE604422CAA3C59F20AD1736F61A
msgctxt ",DAE1EE604422CAA3C59F20AD1736F61A"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Scare me? What? That I would go lost, no I know this park like the back of my hand</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Skrämmer mig? Vad? Att jag skulle gå vilse? Nej, jag känner den här parken som min egen ficka</>"

#. Key:	B5F98CF7413E7A85326DC4920EC97295
msgctxt ",B5F98CF7413E7A85326DC4920EC97295"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Well... Can I go and check out  the tower for myself?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Tja... Kan jag gå och kolla in tornet själv?</>"

#. Key:	11B342884B078F4B31250B818FA1E03F
msgctxt ",11B342884B078F4B31250B818FA1E03F"
msgid "<Speech>Can I go check it out myself?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Kan jag gå och kolla upp det själv?</>"

#. Key:	A8B127A1482006550B95E693B3Kailyn0D63
msgctxt ",A8B127A1482006550B95E693B3Kailyn0D63"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Well... I'm not sure but, I wouldn't want to suspect anything else</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Tja... jag är inte säker, men jag skulle inte vilja misstänka något annat</>"

#. Key:	6720F41145E7C85D5127D599C883BFA8
msgctxt ",6720F41145E7C85D5127D599C883BFA8"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Oh okay, I will keep that in mind.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Åh okej, jag ska ha det i åtanke.</>"

#. Key:	DFB8A5034D95CDDC7BCE528221887593
msgctxt ",DFB8A5034D95CDDC7BCE528221887593"
msgid "<Speech>Okay, I'll keep that in mind</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Okej, jag ska ha det i åtanke</>"

#. Key:	4C3516EB4FB9E9A6E03552B1690D19E1
msgctxt ",4C3516EB4FB9E9A6E03552B1690D19E1"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Well the park is relatively safe, just don't go too close to any of wild life and be careful around the river down East Ridge Trail, if you fall in. We might never see you again.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Parken är relativt säker, gå bara inte för nära några vilda djur och var försiktig vid floden längs East Ridge Trail. Om du faller i kanske vi aldrig ser dig igen.</>"

#. Key:	FF5E8D194EC290F279764ABDA86AEB4E
msgctxt ",FF5E8D194EC290F279764ABDA86AEB4E"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Oh okay... yeah, see you in the morning.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Åh okej... ja, vi ses i morgon bitti.</>"

#. Key:	0C567DCC47357621CD0C508C24C42EDC
msgctxt ",0C567DCC47357621CD0C508C24C42EDC"
msgid "<Speech>Okay, see you in the morning</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Okej, vi ses i morgon bitti</>"

#. Key:	29BCC79841A223B675E062B58C4562EF
msgctxt ",29BCC79841A223B675E062B58C4562EF"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Listen... I wouldn't worry too much about it. It's getting late anyway so I think I'm gonna go to bed. Don't let this keep you up at night, I'll see you in the morning.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Lyssna... jag skulle inte oroa mig för mycket över det. Det börjar ändå bli sent så jag tror jag ska gå och lägga mig. Låt inte det här hålla dig vaken i natt, vi ses i morgon bitti.</>"

#. Key:	5B57A81142619FA74AEC599AF30E7F72
msgctxt ",5B57A81142619FA74AEC599AF30E7F72"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah you're right, I should head to bed too. I'll see you in the morning.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Ja, du har rätt, jag borde också gå och lägga mig. Vi ses i morgon bitti.</>"

#. Key:	2EED89DD49E361DEB2F9DFAC71E8844E
msgctxt ",2EED89DD49E361DEB2F9DFAC71E8844E"
msgid "<Speech>Yeah you're right</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Ja, du har rätt</>"

#. Key:	CD863F25417C35CDC2A790A8F5566A97
msgctxt ",CD863F25417C35CDC2A790A8F5566A97"
msgid "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Good, listen it's getting a bit late. I didn't mean to keep you up, I'm going to go to bed now. I'll see you in the morning, Sam.</>"
msgstr "<Kailyn>Kailyn: </><Speech>Bra, lyssna, det börjar bli lite sent. Jag menade inte att hålla dig vaken, jag går och lägger mig nu. Vi ses i morgon bitti, Sam.</>"

#. Key:	3C4782734E81B0D758C6D3A69C5ECFA8
msgctxt ",3C4782734E81B0D758C6D3A69C5ECFA8"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Oh okay... yeah, see you in the morning</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Åh okej... ja, vi ses i morgon bitti</>"

#. Key:	6D6F488846ACC28D04B2319D39CC7435
msgctxt ",6D6F488846ACC28D04B2319D39CC7435"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah you're right, I should head to bed too. I'll see you in the morning</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Ja, du har rätt, jag borde också gå och lägga mig. Vi ses i morgon bitti</>"

#. Key:	A56282C140986535260499A87DDCA65E
msgctxt ",A56282C140986535260499A87DDCA65E"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>I'm here! I'm here! What's going on!?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Jag är här! Jag är här! Vad händer!?</>"

#. Key:	18D2A97B427DA30A496F27AA401EEE7B
msgctxt ",18D2A97B427DA30A496F27AA401EEE7B"
msgid "<Speech>What's going on!?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Vad händer!?</>"

#. Key:	F3092EDE4BD9B798BC3EC88B3D5B008B
msgctxt ",F3092EDE4BD9B798BC3EC88B3D5B008B"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>CLEARWATER!</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>CLEARWATER!</>"

#. Key:	AD23DF764BC96D181DAE29B0BFD0261C
msgctxt ",AD23DF764BC96D181DAE29B0BFD0261C"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Alright, alright. I'll be on my way!</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Okej, okej. Jag är på väg!</>"

#. Key:	DC23AFA2441E8C1008A72088661B4D5F
msgctxt ",DC23AFA2441E8C1008A72088661B4D5F"
msgid "<Speech>I'll be on my way</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Jag är på väg</>"

#. Key:	FDED660C43306330A7AE22A5729B637B
msgctxt ",FDED660C43306330A7AE22A5729B637B"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Oh there you are!? I HAVE BEEN TRYING TO REACH YOU FOR THE PAST HALF AN HOUR! JUST LOOK SOUTH EAST, YOU'LL SEE A PILAR OF SMOKE, SOME IDIOT HAS STARTED A CAMPFIRE IN THIS HEAT AND YOU SHOULD HAVE BEEN ON YOUR WAY THERE, 30 MINUTES AGO SO YOU BETTER GET GOING...NOW!</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Åh, där är du!? JAG HAR FÖRSÖKT FÅ TAG PÅ DIG I EN HALVTIMME! TITTA BARA SYDOST, DU KOMMER SE EN RÖKPELARE, NÅGON IDIOT HAR STARTAT EN LÄGERELD I DEN HÄR VÄRMEN OCH DU BORDE HA VARIT PÅ VÄG DIT FÖR 30 MINUTER SEDAN, SÅ SÄTT FART... NU!</>"

#. Key:	BBCE8C11491A48A7EFA25BBA19CA2E3A
msgctxt ",BBCE8C11491A48A7EFA25BBA19CA2E3A"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah, I'm here.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Ja, jag är här.</>"

#. Key:	9B4185144E48F42167DC8CAE3ED3A454
msgctxt ",9B4185144E48F42167DC8CAE3ED3A454"
msgid "<Speech>Yeah</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Ja</>"

#. Key:	B99A82C943E6F40437FD38B162427ADF
msgctxt ",B99A82C943E6F40437FD38B162427ADF"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Hello? You there?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Hallå? Är du där?</>"

#. Key:	1AB1893C4B39C886FE061EB490520E02
msgctxt ",1AB1893C4B39C886FE061EB490520E02"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>What do you even get paid for!?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Vad får du ens betalt för!?</>"

#. Key:	0CC256574D80ECF217EDCBB609EB90FB
msgctxt ",0CC256574D80ECF217EDCBB609EB90FB"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Alright, I'm back. Fire's out</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Okej, jag är tillbaka. Elden är släckt</>"

#. Key:	5CF285844B688E95AD5FF98891B2855A
msgctxt ",5CF285844B688E95AD5FF98891B2855A"
msgid "<Speech>Fire's out</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Elden är släckt</>"

#. Key:	60B3C4AE4E965DF7184E2FB885A5559F
msgctxt ",60B3C4AE4E965DF7184E2FB885A5559F"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>There was no one there. I tried calling out but no one answered. It looked like a camp site but it was like the campers had just vanished.  All their stuff was still there.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Det var ingen där. Jag försökte ropa men ingen svarade. Det såg ut som en lägerplats, men det var som om camparna bara hade försvunnit. Alla deras saker låg fortfarande kvar.</>"

#. Key:	DF0083014A5F2A7612BD9D9C2CBD911C
msgctxt ",DF0083014A5F2A7612BD9D9C2CBD911C"
msgid "<Speech>There was no one there</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Det var ingen där</>"

#. Key:	670048E145356D6A991E4C9EC573A890
msgctxt ",670048E145356D6A991E4C9EC573A890"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Good! What did you say to those idiots!?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Bra! Vad sa du till de där idioterna!?</>"

#. Key:	7C6D3AC240C623C2294339834C939C0D
msgctxt ",7C6D3AC240C623C2294339834C939C0D"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah...It was weird, it looked like they shoulda been there but no one was there.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Ja... det var konstigt, det såg ut som att de borde ha varit där men ingen var där.</>"

#. Key:	7A51170242B07536834E23A014AD22FA
msgctxt ",7A51170242B07536834E23A014AD22FA"
msgid "<Speech>Yeah it was weird</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Ja, det var konstigt</>"

#. Key:	1B5BAF9243B713E9752AF6A249D4BCDA
msgctxt ",1B5BAF9243B713E9752AF6A249D4BCDA"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>What?</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Va?</>"

#. Key:	9E5BB45E4C5B68F5325A458AD85C8B6D
msgctxt ",9E5BB45E4C5B68F5325A458AD85C8B6D"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hello?... hello?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hallå?... hallå?</>"

#. Key:	58CDC93248E5FDC5C74AD883861AF634
msgctxt ",58CDC93248E5FDC5C74AD883861AF634"
msgid "<Speech>Hello?... hello?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Hallå?... hallå?</>"

#. Key:	2DA816CE4B66B6C977F08B866D8E590B
msgctxt ",2DA816CE4B66B6C977F08B866D8E590B"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>...</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>...</>"

#. Key:	7304EC49476442E1426B48AE104A36E3
msgctxt ",7304EC49476442E1426B48AE104A36E3"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Oh!? Really?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Åh!? Verkligen?</>"

#. Key:	0C2E10F645328CD48263649CED1A8507
msgctxt ",0C2E10F645328CD48263649CED1A8507"
msgid "<Speech>Oh!? Really?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Åh!? Verkligen?</>"

#. Key:	8186130A4684C6BA091B89A8497B4BDF
msgctxt ",8186130A4684C6BA091B89A8497B4BDF"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Listen, Clearwater. I just got a call in that the hikers abandoned their camp. They'll come back for their stuff later, so you don't have to worry about this anymore. I'll take care of it.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Lyssna, Clearwater. Jag fick precis ett samtal om att vandrarna övergav sitt läger. De kommer tillbaka efter sina saker senare, så du behöver inte oroa dig för det här längre. Jag tar hand om det.</>"

#. Key:	D83CC9FE4D40C4AFDCC6BC9D9C6Kailyn0AA
msgctxt ",D83CC9FE4D40C4AFDCC6BC9D9C6Kailyn0AA"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Oh...okay, yeah you got it.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Åh... okej, ja, uppfattat.</>"

#. Key:	EC24E6AE479A70E5609203B46763957A
msgctxt ",EC24E6AE479A70E5609203B46763957A"
msgid "<Speech>You got it.</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Uppfattat.</>"

#. Key:	DB330B394C98A05090946185BC73CE4E
msgctxt ",DB330B394C98A05090946185BC73CE4E"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Yeah, yeah, don't even think about it. Just go back to whatever you were doing.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Ja, ja, tänk inte ens på det. Gå bara tillbaka till vad du nu gjorde.</>"

#. Key:	71131049481BA5F716C45A849F43B74C
msgctxt ",71131049481BA5F716C45A849F43B74C"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Good, call me if you see any fires. Talk to you later.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Bra, ring mig om du ser några bränder. Vi hörs senare.</>"

#. Key:	DA20ED4641F136KailynC84EE381BDD250AF
msgctxt ",DA20ED4641F136KailynC84EE381BDD250AF"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hello!</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hallå!</>"

#. Key:	CC205120452542E682CFBCB097EDB46F
msgctxt ",CC205120452542E682CFBCB097EDB46F"
msgid "<Speech>Hello!</>"
msgstr "<Speech>Hallå!</>"

