#. Key:	5C005E0F4ED97D3FC41887BF95B7DEE0
msgctxt ",5C005E0F4ED97D3FC41887BF95B7DEE0"
msgid "<Hiker>Park Ranger: </><Speech>Sorry didn't mean scared you. But, what you doing here? You lost?</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>Parkvakt: </><Speech>Förlåt, menade inte att skrämma dig. Men vad gör du här? Är du vilse?</>"

#. Key:	D85AC2EF4A2B1B32F86765B4B3B75287
msgctxt ",D85AC2EF4A2B1B32F86765B4B3B75287"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Kind of? I'm trying to find my way to my tower.</>"
